# On Linux devboxes, ~/.config/nix is a symlink to nix/ inside this repo,
# so home-manager's `xdg.configFile."nix/nix.conf"` (from modules/common.nix)
# materializes its symlink AT /nix/nix.conf inside the working tree. Cosmetic
# pollution only — the symlink target lives in /nix/store/.../home-files/.
/nix/nix.conf
